### Next.js / Frontend
- Prefer RSC (React Server Components) by default — 'use client' only when strictly needed
- Server Actions for all mutations (forms, deletes, updates)
- Route Handlers for REST API endpoints in app/api/
- generateMetadata() on every page for SEO
- always next/image for images, next/font for fonts
- CSS theme variables (--color-*) — never hardcoded colors
- revalidatePath() / revalidateTag() after every mutation
